Package lt.eif.viko.kvisciuna.movieapp.model

Class Movie

java.lang.Object
lt.eif.viko.kvisciuna.movieapp.model.Movie
@Entity public class Movie extends Object
Represents a movie within the movie application. This class is annotated for persistence in a database using JPA and for XML serialization/deserialization with JAXB. It includes properties for the movie's unique identifier, name, length, associated actors, producer, language, and category, demonstrating the use of both one-to-many and one-to-one relationships.
